page.title: 11Clements Tump continued
page.content: TO THE "CHURCH OF ENGLAND SCHOOL"WHICH IS NOT IN USE NOWADAYS.MRS.NASH LEFT SCHOOL AT 14 YEARS OLD,SHE WENT TO BREAM AFTER LEAVING SCHOOL AND LEARNED DRESS MAKING,WHICH SHE WAS VERY SUCCESSFUL WITH AND STILL INSISTS TO MAKE HER OWN CLOTHES TODAY. WHEN SHE WAS MARRIED SHE MOVED TO CLEMENTS END GREEN.CLEMENTS TUMP WAS STILL THE SAME WHEN MRS.NASH GOT MARRIED,EVEN THOUGH THERE MIGHT STILL BE ALOT MORE CHILDREN AROUND.ELEVEN YEARS AGO THE HOUSE MRS.NASH LIVED IN FOR 27 YEARS WAS BLOWN UP BY A GAS EXPLOSION,THERE WAS A MOTHER AND 2 CHILDREN KILLED.IT IS VERY MUCH THE SAME AROUND CLEMENTS TUMP AS IT WAS 72 YEARS AGO,EXCEPT FOR A FEW MORE HOUSES.
